d.min.js\n\/* ]]> *\/\n<\/script>\n",
  "description": "Claim brought by the foreign trustee from Germany against foreign clients who resided here to recover over $800,000 in assets that trustee claimed belonged to an estate in Germany that had filed for bankruptcy. &nbsp;The Trustee claimed that one of my clients murdered the ex-husband of my other client&#8217;s wife. &nbsp;The autopsy report concluded that the husband had committed suicide after being despondent over large losses he suffered in the stock market in October of 1987. I obtained a court order dismissing the cases against clients and recovered court costs for my clients.",
